## GLOBAL UI PATTERNS (Across All Display Ads Pages)

### Common Header Toolbar
```
[Breadcrumb: Display Ads > Section > Sub-section]   [Theme] [Search] [User] [Filter?] [Page Filter?] [Date Range]
```

### Common Table Actions
- **3-dot (⋮) menu** on rows: Edit, Duplicate (and sometimes Delete)
- **Toggle switches**: Enable/Disable rows inline
- **Column customizer**: Show/hide columns
- **Download icon**: Export table data
- **Search inputs**: Per-section search

### Common Modal Patterns
- **Multi-step numbered forms** (1, 2, 3… sections)
- **Confirmation dialogs** on unsaved-changes close: "Your changes will be lost / There are some unsaved changes" → Cancel/No & Yes buttons
- **Required fields** marked with red asterisk `*`
- **Info icons** `ⓘ` on field labels for tooltips
- **Create / Save / Approve / Reject** footer buttons

### Status Values Observed
- Under Review (orange)
- Pending Reviews
- Active / Inactive (toggle)
- Coming Soon (orange text — disabled)
- Beta (badge)
- Alpha (badge)
- NEW (badge)
- Recently Added (ribbon)

